---
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-stone-900">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Food photo -->
      <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="/images/fajitas-table.webp"
            alt="Sizzling fajitas at Habanero Mexican Cafe"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full h-[480px] object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- little tag -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -right-5 bg-red-700 text-white rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow-xl text-center">
          <p class="font-bold text-2xl">27+</p>
          <p class="text-red-200 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Years in Austin</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Story -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <p class="text-orange-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-100 mb-6 leading-tight">
          Family Recipes.<br />
          <span class="italic font-normal">Austin Roots.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-stone-400 leading-relaxed text-base">
          <p>
            Habanero has been a beloved part of Austin for over 27 years. It all started with <strong class="text-stone-200">"Dos Hermanos"</strong> — the restaurant founded by Arturo Ibarra's father and uncle — an institution that old Austinites still talk about with a smile.
          </p>
          <p>
            When the original owners retired, Arturo chose to carry the torch. He bought the remaining location, renamed it Habanero Mexican Cafe, and kept every cherished family recipe exactly as it was. The rest, as they say, was history.
          </p>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="mt-6 border-l-4 border-orange-500 pl-5 text-stone-300 italic text-lg leading-relaxed">
          "We thank you for all the love and support you continue to give to us."
          <footer class="text-sm not-italic font-bold text-stone-500 mt-2">— The Ibarra Family</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-6">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400">🏠</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wide mt-1">Family Owned</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400">🌮</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wide mt-1">Authentic Recipes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400">❤️</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wide mt-1">Austin Since '97</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
